Source.Name: gwyddion
Source.Summary: Free SPM (AFM, SNOM/NSOM, STM, MFM, ...) data analysis software
Source.Description: Gwyddion is a modular program for SPM (scanning probe microscopy) data visualization and analysis. Primarily is is intended for the analysis of height fields obtained by SPM techniques (AFM, MFM, STM, SNOM/NSOM) and it supports a lot of SPM data formats.
